{"tid":2437753,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"甜美公務員PO文「自慰棒壞了」！網友灌爆辱罵　同事冷眼逼到離職","createTime":"2021-03-08T05:27:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T05:39:09.000Z","uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8cdd1569857a2f5940a7afd0fc5a2d75e3ec3220","tid":2437753,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T05:27:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5489/d5489268.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5489%2Fd5489268.jpg&h=711483ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭中央選舉委員會公關主任、30歲的安琪拉（Angela Eremenko）在社群媒體上發文<br />\n，抱怨自慰棒壞掉了，未料引來大批網友留言怒罵，批評字眼不堪入目。她自認遭到嚴重<br />\n網路霸凌，公司和同事卻沒有給予任何支持，由於無法忍受辦公室的不友善氣氛，最後被<br />\n逼得離職。<br />\n <br />\n根據《每日星報》報導，安琪拉表示，故障的自慰棒「震動兩下、閃爍著紅色指示燈，然<br />\n後就不會動了。如果要說這毀了我的第一次還不夠，我把它拿去充電，但卻沒有用」，只<br />\n好和男友回到情趣用品店，最後得以換貨。<br />\n <br />\n安琪拉的貼文意外惹怒社會大眾。網友們氣憤留言，「妳是認真的嗎？一名中央選舉委員<br />\n會的員工？妳可能需要換份工作」、「官員們，你們完全瘋了嗎？」、「找個正常男人來<br />\n愛妳吧！」、「這是我們生活的新現實嗎？她寫得好像在描述一支牙刷一樣」、「如果我<br />\n的女人需要自慰棒，我會很沮喪的」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CDakiqjHQOe/?utm_source=ig_embed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCDakiqjHQOe%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058osqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=2c87cbd0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCDakiqjHQOe%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&h=72193c7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CDakiqjHQOe/?utm_source=ig_embed</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CMAe7lBH28l/?utm_source=ig_embed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCMAe7lBH28l%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058osqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=27b6f12e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCMAe7lBH28l%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&h=3bc8f182\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CMAe7lBH28l/?utm_source=ig_embed</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20210307/1932921.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20210307%2F1932921.htm&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058osqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=1a131ac9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20210307/1932921.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f32295721450318eef91998fc49573d122c43457","tid":2437753,"uid":377617,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T05:28:10.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">她寫得好像在描述一支牙刷一樣</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a9e514df38ea3a32e4e8470bc6cf6740c3396ed","tid":2437753,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T05:28:34.000Z","msg":"想同佢玩sex toy<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05f37b9ea528962625e89dcd76b0e0807787bca","tid":2437753,"uid":66514,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T05:28:44.000Z","msg":"一副眼鏡+10歲"},{"pid":"2adbe66f975453776f7244a6fffc65b5bc81b615","tid":2437753,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T05:29:27.000Z","msg":"想屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f67a4da4aa1de4d71d4c7412184743861f969f0","tid":2437753,"uid":199689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T05:29:46.000Z","msg":"烏克蘭咁守舊㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係妒忌條女夠錢買按摩棒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e3e7750f8df982a9677d25a46bd948178b7025","tid":2437753,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f32295721450318ee